The wreckage of one of the enemy drones fell into the field, and the combat part was immersed deep into the ground.

About thisShe reported March 24National Police of Ukraine.

Another unbearable part of Shahaneda was discovered nearby.

Explosives of police of Dnipropetrovsk region cautiously seized dangerous explosive objects and transported to the displaced area, where they were controlled.

Asreported the armyinform, The forces of defense showed the night of "Shahmed".
title: In Dnipropetrovsk, they disposed of Shahaneda's combat part
